01:13:22,084 --> 01:13:24,921
- [Lou] Our investments have
paid off, haven't they, Darce?

1021
01:13:24,921 --> 01:13:27,509
- [Megan] Lou and Frenchy
have about the same.

1022
01:13:27,509 --> 01:13:30,053
- [Frenchy] People above
thought he was talking too much.

1023
01:13:30,053 --> 01:13:31,514
- [Darcy] You know
I love Lou, right?

1024
01:13:31,514 --> 01:13:34,894
This partnership with
him is killing me.

1025
01:13:34,894 --> 01:13:38,440
- [Ray] Are you gonna
kill me too, Father?

1026
01:13:50,666 --> 01:13:52,460
- What are you doing?

1027
01:13:54,296 --> 01:13:55,298
- I'm going.

1028
01:14:00,012 --> 01:14:02,265
- Where are you going, Ray?

1029
01:14:11,904 --> 01:14:13,448
- What are you doing?

1030
01:14:13,448 --> 01:14:15,326
- I'm not sitting around here
while you get yourself killed.

1031
01:14:17,203 --> 01:14:19,457
I'm going back to the police
station to back up the files

1032
01:14:19,457 --> 01:14:21,459
so nobody erases them.

1033
01:14:21,459 --> 01:14:23,503
- Hey, that's a
really good idea,

1034
01:14:23,503 --> 01:14:25,047
but I don't want you doing it.

1035
01:14:25,047 --> 01:14:26,758
Now come on, this is very
personal to me right now.

1036
01:14:26,758 --> 01:14:28,260
This is between me and Lou.

1037
01:14:28,260 --> 01:14:30,137
I don't want you involved.

1038
01:14:30,137 --> 01:14:32,099
- I'm already involved, Ray.

1039
01:14:32,099 --> 01:14:33,226
They want me dead too.

1040
01:14:35,061 --> 01:14:38,066
Besides, I'll be at the police
station where I can be safer.

1041
01:14:43,782 --> 01:14:45,326
- Know how to use one of these?

1042
01:14:47,496 --> 01:14:49,123
- Yeah.

1043
01:14:49,123 --> 01:14:51,126
- The safety's on, take it.

1044
01:15:57,134 --> 01:15:59,137
- [Frenchy] I can't
believe you came back, Ray.

1045
01:16:00,889 --> 01:16:02,726
I thought you were
smarter than that.

1046
01:16:05,521 --> 01:16:06,898
You may not be in New York,

1047
01:16:08,359 --> 01:16:10,778
but you're way out of
your league, mon ami.

1048
01:16:12,072 --> 01:16:12,990
Welcome home.

1049
01:16:21,252 --> 01:16:25,173
- You're gonna wish I
never came back, Frenchy.

1050
01:16:26,550 --> 01:16:28,345
When you shot my brother,
you killed yourself.

1051
01:16:33,727 --> 01:16:36,648
(gunshots banging)

1052
01:16:55,883 --> 01:16:58,804
(gunshots banging)

1053
01:17:24,924 --> 01:17:27,219
(gunshot banging)
(Blue shouting)

1054
01:17:27,219 --> 01:17:30,181
(gunshots banging)

1055
01:17:40,237 --> 01:17:43,157
(gunshots banging)

1056
01:19:00,349 --> 01:19:03,312
(gunshots banging)

1057
01:19:12,700 --> 01:19:13,909
(gunshot banging)

1058
01:19:13,909 --> 01:19:16,580
(siren blaring)

1059
01:19:37,151 --> 01:19:38,736
- I'm standing behind you, Ray.

1060
01:19:40,071 --> 01:19:41,072
Drop your guns.

1061
01:19:48,917 --> 01:19:50,294
It's all been said before.

1062
01:19:52,297 --> 01:19:53,715
There's nothing more to say.

1063
01:19:55,802 --> 01:19:56,636
- Wrong.

1064
01:19:59,182 --> 01:20:00,892
Drop the guns or I drop you.

1065
01:20:03,062 --> 01:20:03,896
Now!

1066
01:20:13,535 --> 01:20:14,369
One.

1067
01:20:16,289 --> 01:20:17,123
Two.

1068
01:20:20,294 --> 01:20:21,128
Three.

1069
01:20:21,128 --> 01:20:22,130
(gunshot banging)

1070
01:20:22,130 --> 01:20:25,093
(kick thudding)
(Frenchy groans)

1071
01:20:25,093 --> 01:20:25,927
- Run!

1072
01:20:30,433 --> 01:20:33,354
(gunshots banging)

1073
01:20:43,827 --> 01:20:44,661
Geez.

1074
01:20:46,247 --> 01:20:48,166
Gimme the gun.

1075
01:20:48,166 --> 01:20:51,129
Are you okay?
- Yeah, yeah, are you?

1076
01:21:30,350 --> 01:21:31,936
- What are you doing here?

1077
01:21:31,936 --> 01:21:32,938
- You're welcome.

1078
01:21:32,938 --> 01:21:34,523
- I can't believe you shot him.

1079
01:21:35,650 --> 01:21:37,026
- I said I would.

1080
01:21:37,026 --> 01:21:38,320
- That you did.

1081
01:21:40,657 --> 01:21:43,619
(gunshots banging)

1082
01:21:58,724 --> 01:22:00,101
We can't stay here too long.

1083
01:22:01,978 --> 01:22:02,813
Oh geez.

1084
01:22:05,483 --> 01:22:07,444
- What are you doing?
What are you doing?

1085
01:22:08,779 --> 01:22:09,739
- There's some gas in there.

1086
01:22:09,739 --> 01:22:11,074
I hope there's enough.

1087
01:22:11,074 --> 01:22:12,033
Hey, take my tourniquet off.

1088
01:22:12,033 --> 01:22:13,077
- What?

1089
01:22:13,077 --> 01:22:14,246
Oh god.
- Just take it off.

1090
01:22:14,246 --> 01:22:16,248
- Oh god, oh god, there.

1091
01:22:21,589 --> 01:22:22,423
Careful.

1092
01:22:22,423 --> 01:22:25,344
(gunshots banging)

1093
01:22:29,099 --> 01:22:32,020
(gunshots banging)

1094
01:22:36,777 --> 01:22:40,490
- Oh, damn it, I shouldn't
have quit smoking.

1095
01:22:40,490 --> 01:22:42,160
- Here, here, here.

1096
01:22:42,160 --> 01:22:43,161
- You smoke?

1097
01:22:49,628 --> 01:22:50,838
- Gimme that.
- Damn it.

1098
01:22:50,838 --> 01:22:52,715
Try to get it there.

1099
01:22:52,715 --> 01:22:53,926
- [Megan] There, I got it.

1100
01:22:53,926 --> 01:22:54,843
That's it, it's going.

1101
01:22:54,843 --> 01:22:57,264
- Okay, now run like heck, go.

1102
01:23:01,562 --> 01:23:05,025
(gunshots banging)

1103
01:23:05,025 --> 01:23:07,695
(dramatic music)

1104
01:23:24,969 --> 01:23:25,971
- Oh my god.

1105
01:23:28,265 --> 01:23:30,227
(explosion booming)

1106
01:23:30,227 --> 01:23:33,189
(Frenchy shouting)

1107
01:23:46,500 --> 01:23:47,334
- Megan?

1108
01:23:59,976 --> 01:24:01,771
- I remember teaching
you how to use that.

1109
01:24:08,488 --> 01:24:12,286
Hurts like hell,
but I'm still alive.

1110
01:24:24,719 --> 01:24:25,554
- You all right?

1111
01:24:31,938 --> 01:24:35,401
- It's the final
scene, huh, Ray?

1112
01:24:35,401 --> 01:24:36,485
Father against son.

1113
01:24:39,865 --> 01:24:42,869
- No, Lou, no.

1114
01:24:44,997 --> 01:24:46,959
Father against himself.

1115
01:25:05,151 --> 01:25:06,862
Megan and I are
walking out of here.

1116
01:25:11,702 --> 01:25:12,620
- I don't think so.

1117
01:25:22,717 --> 01:25:27,724
- Trust me, he won't shoot you.

1118
01:25:45,624 --> 01:25:46,751
- Don't move.

1119
01:26:09,908 --> 01:26:11,493
Ray, don't test me.

1120
01:26:15,541 --> 01:26:16,375
Ray.

1121
01:26:18,587 --> 01:26:19,421
Ray!

1122
01:26:22,092 --> 01:26:22,926
Ray!

1123
01:26:25,054 --> 01:26:25,888
Ray!

1124
01:26:46,042 --> 01:26:46,877
Ray!

1125
01:26:49,839 --> 01:26:51,466
I'm sorry.

1126
01:26:51,466 --> 01:26:52,259
Darcy!

1127
01:26:57,266 --> 01:26:58,101
Darcy.

1128
01:27:43,497 --> 01:27:46,210
(dramatic music)

1129
01:32:29,564 --> 01:32:32,485
(triumphant music)

